<subSubSection id="C368652E93508E0DF2AAFDD6FB55FD4A" pageId="9" pageNumber="493" type="description">
<paragraph id="8BCD36A593508E0DF2AAFDD6FB55FD4A" blockId="9.[151,1436,580,780]" pageId="9" pageNumber="493">
<materialsCitation id="3B1A3CF893508E0DF2AAFDD6FB51FD4A" ID-GBIF-Occurrence="3798147320" collectorName="J. Serrano" pageId="9" pageNumber="493" specimenCount="2" typeStatus="lectotype">
The specimen here designated as 
<typeStatus id="54C9880793508E0DF035FDD6FDBEFD95" box="[520,623,580,606]" pageId="9" pageNumber="493">lectotype</typeStatus>
is a male bearing the labels: “ 
<taxonomicName id="4C724D2693508E0DF185FDD6FB81FD95" authorityName="Dejean" authorityYear="1829" box="[952,1104,580,606]" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Harpalus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="9" pageNumber="493" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="subquadratus">
<emphasis id="B906EAB793508E0DF185FDD6FB81FD95" box="[952,1104,580,606]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="493">subquadratus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
m. in Gallia merid.”, “Aude.” and “ 
<typeStatus id="54C9880793508E0DF2EDFDF5FE92FD4A" box="[208,323,615,641]" pageId="9" pageNumber="493">Lectotype</typeStatus>
of 
<taxonomicName id="4C724D2693508E0DF355FDF5FC5CFD4A" authority="Dejean, 1829" authorityName="Dejean" authorityYear="1829" box="[360,909,615,641]" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Harpalus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="9" pageNumber="493" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="subquadratus" subGenus="Ophonus">
<emphasis id="B906EAB793508E0DF355FDF5FD21FD4A" box="[360,752,615,641]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="493">Harpalus (Ophonus) subquadratus</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B5493508E0DF0CAFDF5FC5CFD4A" author="Dejean, P. F. M. A." box="[759,909,615,641]" pageId="9" pageNumber="493" refId="ref10732" refString="Dejean, P. F. M. A. (1829) Species general des coleopteres de la collection de M. le Comte Dejean. Tome quatrieme. Mequignon- Marvis, Paris, vii + 520 pp." type="book" year="1829">Dejean, 1829</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
desig. by 
<collectorName id="2687537393508E0DF63DFDFAFBA7FD4A" box="[1024,1142,615,642]" pageId="9" pageNumber="493">J. Serrano</collectorName>
”
</materialsCitation>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="C368652E93508E0DF2FAFD18FBBBFCC7" pageId="9" pageNumber="493" type="description">
<paragraph id="8BCD36A593508E0DF2FAFD18FD22FD22" blockId="9.[151,1436,580,780]" pageId="9" pageNumber="493">
<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B5493508E0DF2FAFD18FEB9FD6F" author="Dejean, P. F. M. A." box="[199,360,650,676]" pageId="9" pageNumber="493" refId="ref10732" refString="Dejean, P. F. M. A. (1829) Species general des coleopteres de la collection de M. le Comte Dejean. Tome quatrieme. Mequignon- Marvis, Paris, vii + 520 pp." type="book" year="1829">Dejean (1829)</bibRefCitation>
probably studied a number of specimens of 
<taxonomicName id="4C724D2693508E0DF160FD18FBC9FD6F" authorityName="Dejean" authorityYear="1829" box="[861,1048,650,676]" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Harpalus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="9" pageNumber="493" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="subquadratus">
<emphasis id="B906EAB793508E0DF160FD18FBC9FD6F" box="[861,1048,650,676]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="493">O. subquadratus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
as he stated that: 
<emphasis id="B906EAB793508E0DF6DFFD18FE77FD0D" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="493">
Il se trouve dans le midi de la 
<collectingCountry id="F365763593508E0DF317FD3FFEAAFD0D" box="[298,379,685,710]" name="France" pageId="9" pageNumber="493">France</collectingCountry>
...
</emphasis>
The current concept of the species matches the characters shown by the 
<typeStatus id="54C9880793508E0DF6EAFD3EFA90FD0D" box="[1239,1345,684,710]" pageId="9" pageNumber="493">lectotype</typeStatus>
, as seen in 
<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B5493508E0DF289FD5DFE8DFD22" author="Jeannel, R." box="[180,348,719,745]" pageId="9" pageNumber="493" pagination="572 - 1173" refId="ref11231" refString="Jeannel, R. (1942) Coleopteres carabiques. Deuxieme partie. Faune de France 40. Librairie de la Faculte des Sciences, Paris, pp. 572 - 1173." type="book chapter" year="1942">Jeannel (1942)</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B5493508E0DF355FD5DFE2DFD22" author="Sciaky, R." box="[360,508,719,745]" pageId="9" pageNumber="493" pagination="29 - 120" refId="ref12184" refString="Sciaky, R. (1987) Revisione delle specie paleartiche occidentali del genere Ophonus Dejean, 1821. Memoria della Societa Entomologica Italiana, 65, 29 - 120." type="journal article" year="1987">Sciaky, 1987</bibRefCitation>
), 
<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B5493508E0DF032FD42FD71FD22" author="Wrase, D. W." box="[527,672,719,746]" pageId="9" pageNumber="493" pagination="344 - 386" refId="ref12516" refString="Wrase, D. W. (2004) Harpalina. In: Freude, H., Harde, K. W., Lohse, G. A. &amp; Klausnitzer, B. (Eds.), Die Kafer Mitteleuropas. Bd. 2 Adephaga 1: Carabidae (Laufkafer). Spektrum-Verlag, Heidelberg / Berlin, pp. 344 - 386." type="book chapter" year="2004">Wrase (2004</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B5493508E0DF096FD5DFD36FD22" author="Wrase, D. W." box="[683,743,719,745]" pageId="9" pageNumber="493" refId="ref12634" refString="Wrase, D. W. (2011) Genus Tschitscherinellus. Arndt, E., Schnitter, P., Sfenthourakis, S. &amp; Wrase, D. W. (Eds.), Ground beetles (Carabidae) of Greece. Pensoft, Sofia, pp. 163." type="book" year="2011">2011</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BCD36A593508E0DF2FAFD60FBBBFCC7" blockId="9.[151,1436,580,780]" box="[199,1130,754,780]" pageId="9" pageNumber="493">
It is distributed in the Mediterranean Basin and to the east it reaches 
<collectingCountry id="F365763593508E0DF1F5FD60FBB7FCC7" box="[968,1126,754,780]" name="Turkmenistan" pageId="9" pageNumber="493">Turkmenistan</collectingCountry>
.
</paragraph>
